text:
The #TrumpBudget will only hurt Americans &amp; will:

👩‍🎓Cut $170 BILLION from student loan programs;
🧓Cut $24 BILLION from Social Security; &amp;
🧱Spend $2 BILLION on a useless border wall.

The President’s budget is the latest example of his broken promises to working Americans.

As we begin the 2nd session of the 116th Congress today, I remain committed to proposing &amp; voting on bills that will: 

💊 lower health care costs &amp; prescription drug prices;
💸 increase high-paying jobs;
 🏗️rebuild America's infrastructure; 

For the #TX15 &amp; #ForThePeople.
